Emalunga eMkhandlu Wetifundza waseWales akhatsatekile ngekutsi utawubonakala angumuntfu longatsandvwa.
Lamanye emalunga aleSigungu aphikisana nesincumo sekugucula ligama lawo abe yi-MWP (Latin: I-MP yase Wales).
Loku kuhambisana nesifiso sekugucula ligama leSigungu sibe yiPhalamende yase Wales.
Emalunga aleSigungu akhatsatekile ngekutsi loku kutawubangela kutsi bahlekwe.
Lelinye lilunga le-LAB labekacabanga kutsi licembu lakhe liyakhatsateka ngekutsi loku kuhambisana ne-LWTP ne-LWTP.
Kubafundzi labangasibo baseWelsh: twp kusho silima ngesiWelsh kantsi pwp kusho khakhakhak.
Lelinye lilunga leSigungu saVelonkhe latsi lonkhe licembu alijabuli futsi laphakamisa letinye tindlela.
Umgcini we Welsh watsi licembu lakhe belimukele lolushintjo, kodvwa watsi bekusishintjo lesincane lesisuka ku-MWP siye ku-Lel.
Phela leligama lelitsi w lisetjentiswa ngendlela lefanako neligama lelitsi u lelisetjentiswa e-Yorkshire.
LiKhomishane leSigungu lesengamele, lelisungula imitsetfo yekugucula emagama, latsi: Kuncuma kwekugcina ngemagama awo onkhe emalunga aleSigungu kutawuba yintfo yemalunga.
Umtsetfo weHulumende wase Wales wanga-2017 waniketa Sigungu seSive sase Wales lilungelo lekugucula ligama laso.
NgaJuni, liKhomishane lamemetela imiphumela yelukhetfo lolwentiwe ngemphakamiso lebeyinesekela lelicinile lekubita leNdlu ngekutsi yiPhalamende yaseWales.
Mayelana nekukhetsa emalunga aleSigungu, liKhomishane lakhetsa emalunga eWelsh Parliament nobe ema-WMP, kodvwa ema-WMP atfola kwesekelwa lokukhulu ngesikhatsi sekubonisana nemphakatsi.
Emalunga aleSigungu aveta ngalokucacile letinye tindlela, kepha kutfola sivumelwano kungaba yindzaba lebuhlungu ku-Elin Jones, lowengamele, lotawutfumela tichibiyelo temitsetfo ngemaviki lambalwa.
Imitsetfo lehlongotwako itawufaka ekhatsi letinye tingucuko emsebentini weSigungu, kufaka ekhatsi imitsetfo yekukhishwa kwemalunga eSigungu kanye neluhlelo lwemtimba welikomiti.
Ngesikhatsi sekubonisana ngemitsetfo, emalunga aleSigungu atawuba neligunya lekuba nemagama abo.
