Nanobe i-Save the Children ilungiselela licembu lekuya ePalu, akukabonakali kutsi tisebenti tasemaveni angaphandle titawuba khona yini.
Satopo, losikhulumi se-National Disaster Agency, watsi tiphatsimandla tase-Indonesia tiyabuka simo ePalu kute titfole kutsi ngabe tinhlangano temave emhlaba titawuvunyelwa yini kusita.
Njengobe i-Indonesia ivame kutfola kutamatama kwemhlaba, live lisengakalilungeli kahle.
