Kodvwa kulamalanga letako, iRosa itawuletsa imvula lenkhulu enyakatfo yeMexico kanye naseningizimu-nshonalanga yeMelika.
Kusukela nga-5 ekuseni ngeLisontfo, Rose wahamba emakhilomitha langu-137 ngehora njengesiphepho lesingaba sigaba-1 futsi wahamba emakhilomitha langu-620 eningizimu-nshonalanga yeCape Euchenia, eMexico.
