Ngaleso sikhatsi, indzawo lenkhulu lenemandla lenemandla lencane icalisa kwakheka elugwini loluse Pacific, futsi iya ngasemphumalanga, ngaselugwini lolusentshonalanga yeMelika, njengobe iRosa itawufika eCalifornia ngeMsombuluko njengesiphepho, itawucala kuhambisa emanti lamanyenti enyakatfo, eningizimu-nshonalanga yeMelika.
NgaMsombuluko, iRosa itawubangela imvula lengemasentimitha langu-25 etindzaweni letitsite taseMexico.
Lomkhatsi lowesabekako lohlangene nalomkhatsi lomkhulu losondzela utawuletsa imvula lenkhulu eningizimu-nshonalanga kulamalanga letako.
Esikhundleni saloko, imvula lencane lengaba ngemasentimitha langu-2,5 kuya kulangu-10 itawubangela tikhukhula letingaba yingoti, umonakalo lomkhulu kanye nekukhukhuleka kwemhlaba.
Lamagelebisi lamanyenti asezindaweni letishisako, ikakhulukati eningizimu yeNevada nase-Arizona, atawukhokha imvula lengangemasentimitha lasihlanu kuya kulasiphohlongo ngelihora.
Kunemvula lencane lengaba ngemasentimitha langu-58 eningizimu-nshonalanga, ikakhulukati endzaweni lenkhulu yase-Arizona.
Lendlela yemvula yetitfwatfwa ingenta kube netikhukhula letiphutfumako kanye netimo letigucuka ngekushesha.
Nangabe kunesiphepho lesesabekako, kungaba liphutsa lelikhulu kuhamba ngetinyawo uye ehlane.
Imvula lenkhulu ingenta kutsi imihosha ibe nemifula lenemandla, bese kutsi umoya lomkhulu uholele etulu.
Lendzawo lenkhulu lenemphimo lephasi letawufika itawuletsa imvula lenkhulu endzaweni letsite lephakeme eningizimu yeCalifornia.
Kungenteka kube nemvula lengetulu kwesentimitha yinye, lokungabangela kutsi kube nematje lamancane futsi nemigwaco ingashona.
Loku kutawuba yimvula yekucala yetikhatsi temvula kulesigodzi.
Letinye tetimvula letinemandla titawungena e-Arizona ngeLisontfo ntsambama nangekuseni ngeMsombuluko bese kutsi emvula inyakaze ngeMsombuluko nangesitsatfu ntsambama.
