Nga-October kutawuba nekushisa lokunyenti eMelika ngenca yekubandza e-Arctic, kodvwa kutawuba kushisa kakhulu etindzaweni letishisako.
Ngaletinye tikhatsi loko kubangela kushintja lokukhulu lokwenteka etindzaweni letincane.
NgeLisontfo, kwaba nemehluko lomkhulu wekushisa eMelika lesemkhatsini.
Kushisa lokukhulu e-Kansas City, Missouri, nase-Omaha, Nebraska, kwehluke ngemashumi lamabili emaCelsius (emaCelsius angu-20°C) kunaseSt. Louis nase-Di Moine, e-Iowa.
Kulindzeleke kutsi kushisa kwasehlobo kuphindze kuvuseleleke etindzaweni letinyenti kulamalanga lambalwa letako.
Emazinga ekushisa lasetulu langetulu kwa-27°C, kulindzeleke kutsi afike etindzaweni letinyenti letisenkabeni nasemphumalanga yeMelika, kusukela e-Great Southern Plains kuya enyakatfo-mpumalanga.
Emuva ngeLesibili, emazinga ekushisa aseNew York atawukhuphuka aze afike ku-27°C, lokusho kutsi kutawuba ngu-10°C ngetulu kwemkhawulo.
