Bantfu labangetulu kwetigidzi letingu-20 babukele tinkhulumo letibuhlungu teMengameli Brett Kavanaugh, kanye netinsolo ta Christine Blasey Ford tekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicasi ngabo-1980 ngetincwadzi letisitfupha teTV ngaLesine.
Kodvwa, lokuchumana kwachubeka ngesikhatsi tinkhampani te-TV tiyekela kusakata ngetindzaba letetayelekile ngenca yalokunye lokwenteka ngaLesihlanu: Umseneti wase-Arizona wenta sivumelwano sekutsi i-FBI icwaninge ngetinsolo letenteka liviki lonkhe.
