Kavanaugh wafakaza ngelulaka watsi uyaciniseka kutsi bekungasiko.
Nielsen watsi ngaLesihlanu, kungenteka kutsi bantfu labangetulu kwetigidzi letingu-20,4 babukele loluhlelo.
Lenkapani icubungule linani lebantfu lebebabukele loluhlelo ku-CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel naku-MSNBC.
Letinombolo betingatfolakali masinyane kulamanye ema-networks, kufaka ekhatsi PBS, C-SPAN kanye Fox Business Network.
Ngetulu kwaloko, Nielsen uvame kuba nebumatima ekubaleni bantfu lababukela ithelevishini emahhovisini.
Kute ngicondze kahle, lesi sibalo sebantfu lesilingana nesebantfu labakhona emdlalweni welibhola letinyawo nobe emkhosini we-Oscar.
Nielsen ubike kutsi Fox News Channel, lebeyisekela kakhulu kukhetfwa kwaKavanaugh, yahola yonkhe inethiwekhi, ngesikhatsi kubukwa bantfu labatigidzi letingu 5,69 ngesikhatsi selicala lelidze.
I-ABC, lebeyibukele imibukiso yetindzaba letitinkhulungwane letingu 3,26, yaba yincenye yesibili.
 Nielsen ibike kutsi i-CBS yatfola tigidzi letingu 3,1, i-NBC yatfola tigidzi letingu 2,94, i-MSNBC yatfola tigidzi letingu 2,89 kantsi i-CNN yatfola tigidzi letingu 2,52.
