Bantfu labanyenti bafa kulesitfwatfwa semhlaba kanye nasetsunami e-Indonesia
Baphatsi babika kutsi bantfu labangu-384 babulawa, labanyenti babo babulawa ngemagagasi lamakhulu labekashaya lwandle ngesikhatsi kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kanye ne-tsunami kuhlasela sihlenge sase-Indonesia i-Sulawesi.
Bantfu labanyenti bebahlangene ePalu, ePitoli, ngaLesihlanu ngesikhatsi emagagasi laphakeme ngemamitha langu-6 agubha emanti, futsi labanyenti bafa ngekukhotsa futsi babulala konkhe lebebakubona endleleni.
Ngemuva kwalesitsunami, kwaba nekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokungu-7.5.
"Ngesikhatsi kushubhisa nge-tsunami kushona, bantfu bebaselugwini futsi abazange babaleke masinyane, ngako baba bahlukunyetwa", kusho sitfunywa se-BNPB, i-Indonesia Disaster Mitigation Agency, Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, enkhulumeni yelucwaningo eJakarta.
"Lentfutfu-mhlaba ayizange itibulale yodvwa, yadvonsa timoto, tingodvo, tindlu, yashaya konkhe lokwakusemhlabatsini", kusho Nugroho, futsi wachubeka watsi ngaphambi kwekutsi ishaye lolwandle, lenfutfu-mhlaba yayihamba ngemakhilomitha langu-800 ngelihora.
Watsi labanye bantfu bebakhuphukela etihlahleni kute babalekele ema-tsunami futsi baphila.
Bantfu labangu-16 700 batfunyelwa etindzaweni letise-24 ePalu.
Titfombe te-Aerial letivela ku-Ejensi Yetehlakalo Letingabonakali, tikhombisa kutsi takhiwo letinyenti kanye netitolo kubhujisiwe, emabhuloho agobekile futsi abhidlikele, futsi lisontfo litungeletwe ngemanti.
NgaLesihlanu, lelidolobha leliselugwini lwalelive lachubeka nekuhlaselwa.
Letichingi tetintsaba betivakala endzaweni lenebantfu labangu-2,4 wetigidzi.
I-Indonesian Technology Assessment and Application Agency (BPPT) yati kutsi emandla lakhishwa kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu ngaLesihlanu, abenemandla langetulu kwa-200 kunemandla elibhomu le-athomu lelahlwa eHiroshima ngesikhatsi seMphi Yelive Yesibili.
Kubikwa kutsi kungenteka kutsi lamagagasi asheshe ashaye kakhulu ngenca yekutsi lelidolobha lisendzaweni lendze, lefinyele kakhulu.
Nugroho wachaza umonakalo ngekutsi "mkhulu" futsi watsi tinkhulungwane tetindlu, tibhedlela, timakethe kanye nemahhotela kwabhidlika.
Watsi imitimba yaletinye tilwane yatfolakala ibhajwe ngaphansi kwetakhiwo letiwile, futsi watsi bantfu labangu-540 balimala futsi labangu-29 abekho.
Nugroho watsi linani lebantfu lababulewe ngulesifo kanye nemonakalo kungenteka kutsi kukhulu ngaselugwini lolungemakhilomitha langu-300 enyakatfo yePalu endzaweni lebitwa ngekutsi yiDongala, lesedvute nendzawo lokwenteka kuyo lokuzamazama kwemhlaba.
Nugroho watsi tinkhombandlela tekuchumana betikhubazekile, ngako-ke kute kwatiswa lokwatfolwa nguDongola.
"Bantfu labangetulu kwa-300 000 bahlala khona", kusho sikhulumi seNhlangano ye-Red Cross, lesitsi tisebenti netisebenti tekutitsandzela titakuya etindzaweni letineligciwane.
Kutsiwa loku sekulihlazo, kodvwa kungenteka kube kubi kakhulu.
NgaMgcibelo, i-Agency yagceka kakhulu ngekungabiketi kutsi i-tsunami ishaye iPala, nanobe tiphatsimandla tatsi lamagagasi afika ngemuva kwekwetfulwa kwesicwayiso.
Kuloluhlu lolutsandvwako lolwabiwa kubantfu labasemabonakude, indvodza lebeyisetulu kulendlu letsite beyingase ivakale ikhala ngemtsunami lobekatako kubantfu lebebasemgwacweni longentasi.
Ngemuva kwemizuzu lembalwa, emanti ayafika asuse takhiwo netimoto.
I-Reuters ayikhoni kuvuma ngekushesha kutsi loku bekubukwe yini.
