I-USA kufanele iphindzaphindze kabili imali yayo yekusekela i-AI
"Njengobe iChina ichubeka nekusebenta ngekuhlakanipha, i-USA kufanele iphindzaphindze kabili imali leyisebentisako ekucwaningeni ngalokwakhiwe", kusho umtsengi kanye nesati sekuhlakanipha lokwakhiwe ngu-Kai-Fu Lee, lowasebenta ku-Google, Microsoft kanye ne-Apple.
Letimphendvulo titfolwe ngemuva kwekutsi tikhungo letehlukene tahulumende waseMelika tikhiphe imibiko lemayelana ne-AI, nanobe i-USA ingenaso sitatimende se-AI.
Ngakulokunye, iChina yalingisa umnyaka lowengcile ngeluhlelo lwayo  lwekuba ngumholi wetintfo letinsha tebuhlakani lobwentiwe nga-2030.
Kuphindza kabili imali yelucwaningo ngebuhlakani bekungasicala lesihle, uma ucabanga kutsi onkhe lamanye emave asadlulile eMelika futsi kulindzeleke lenye intfutfuko yebuhlakani bebuhlakani  , kusho Lee.
Kucetula imali kungenta kube matima kutsi lolunye luhlelo lolukhulu lwekwenta tintfo ngebuhlakani bube seMelika, njengobe Lee asho kulengcoco neCNBC kuleliviki.
Lee, lonencwadzi yakhe letsi "The Artificial Intelligence Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" leyabhalwa nguHoughton Mifflin Harcourt kulenyanga, ungumcondzisi jikelele weSinovation Ventures, lebeke imali ku-Face ++ yinye yetinkampani letatiwako te-AI eChina.
Ngesikhatsi aseCarnegie Mellon University ngemnyaka wa 1980, wasebenta ngendlela yekuhlakanipha lokufakelwako leyaphumelela umlingisi waseMelika lomkhulu kakhulu, Othello, wase uba ngumholi we-Microsoft Research futsi waba ngumengameli we-Google China.
Lee wavuma imincintiswano yangaphambilini ye-US Government Technology, lefana ne-Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency's Robotics Challenge, futsi wabuta kutsi kutawuba nini lolunye luhlolo kute asite kutfola bantfu labanekucondza lokunyenti.
Lee watsi bososayensi baseMelika bavame kucindzeteleka kute batfole imali yahulumende.
"Akusiko kutsi iChina iyasusa baholi betemfundvo, kepha iyasusa tinkampani", kwasho Lee.
Facebook, Google naletinye tinkampani tebucwepheshe eminyakeni lembalwa leyengcile, tiqashe bantfu labanelwati kakhulu labasemanyuvesi kutsi basebente ngekuhlakanipha.
Lee watsi kugucuka kwenchubomgomo yetekufika kungaphindze kusite i-USA kutsi icinise imitamo yayo yekusebentisa buhlakani lobungekwemvelo.
"Ngicabanga kutsi bafundzi labaphotfule ticu tebuhlakani bekute muntfu labatifunela emakhadi laluhlata", washo njalo.
NgaJulayi 2017, Umkhandlu Wesive wase-China wakhipha luhlelo lwekutfutfukisa buhlakani lobusha lobwentiwa bantfu.
Ngetulu kwaloko, Lee watsi, i-National Science Foundation yase-China yenta imali yetisebenti tetemfundvo, njengobe i-National Science Foundation naletinye tinhlangano tahulumende tenta imali yetisebenti tetemfundvo tase-USA, kodvwa lizinga lemsebenti wetemfundvo eChina liphansi.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, Litiko Letekuvikela laseMelika lasungula sikhungo lesihlangene sebuhlakani lobwentiwe, lokwakhiwa  ngekuhlanganisa balingani betimboni netemfundvo, futsi iWhite House yamemetela kutsi kutawakhiwa liKomidi leLincane lebuhlakani lobwentiwe.
Kulenyanga, i-DARPA, i-Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency, yamemetela kutsi itawutsatsa imali lecishe ibe tigidzigidzi letimbili temadola kutsi isekele luhlelo lwe-AI Next.
I-NSF nyalo seyifaka imali lengetulu kwetigidzi letilikhulu temadola ngemnyaka ekucwaningeni ngebuhlakani lobwentiwe.
Kodvwa tinyanga letilandzelako, kute lokwentiwe mayelana nemtsetfo waseMelika lofuna kwakhiwa kweKhomishini Yekuphepha Kwesive lemayelana nebuhlakani bekwenta.
Bantfu baseMacedonia bayavota ngekutsi batsatse libito lelitsite
Bantfu baseMacedonia bavotele kuvota ngeLisontfo kutsi ngabe lifanele yini lishintje ligama lelive libe yiRiphabliki yaseNyakatfo yeMacedonia, lokusho kutsi loko kutawuba yindlela yekulungisa kungcubutana lokutsatse emashumi eminyaka neGreece, lokwavimbela kufinyelela kwayo ku EU nase NATO.
I-Greece, lehlala esifundzeni saseMacedonia, itsi ligama lalomakhelwane wayo wasenyakatfo lisho kutsi inemabango endzawo yaseGreece futsi yavimbela iMacedonia kutsi ingene ku-NATO nase-EU.
NgaJune bohulumende lababili bavumelana ngeligama lelisha, kodvwa bantfu labaphikisako labangemave ngemave batsi kuguculwa kweligama kutawulimata buve bebantfu baseMacedonia labanyenti labangemaSlav.
Umengameli George Ivanov utsi angeke avote kule-referendum, kantsi umkhankaso wekubukela phansi lomhlangano uveta kungabata kutsi lizinga lekuvota litawutfola yini lokungenani lokungu-50% lokudzingekile kute le-referendum isebente.
Umbuto wenhlolovo lowehla elucwebini lwekubhala: Uyasekela yini kungena e-NATO nase-EU uma ngabe usekela sivumelwano neGreece?
Basekeli baloku kuguculwa kwelibito, lokufaka ekhatsi Ndvunankhulu Zoran Zaev, batsi iMacedonia, lelinye lemave lavela ngemuva kwekubhujiswa kweYugoslavia, kufanele ikhokhe intengo yekuba lilunga lemibuso lefana ne-EU ne-NATO.
"Lamuhla ngitewuvota ngelikusasa lelive, ngebantfu labasha baseMacedonia, kute bakwati kuphila ngekukhululeka, bavikelwe yi-European Union, ngobe kusho kuphila lokuphephile kitsi sonkhe", kusho Olivera Georgijevska, 79, eSkopje.
Nanobe kungakafaneli kutsi kube nemtsetfo, emalunga lamanyenti ePhalamende atsi atawugcina imiphumela yelivoto futsi ayente ibe ngulokuncono.
Kuguculwa kweligama kutawudzinga linyenti lemalunga ePhalamende langulokubili kulokutsatfu.
LiKhomishani Lekukhetsa laVelonkhe latsi kute umbiko wekutsi kukhona lokubi lokwentiwe nga-1:00 ntsambama.
Nanobe kunjalo, kuba khona kwebavoti kwabalelwa kumaphesenti langu-16 kuphela, lokucatsanisa neliphesenti lelingu-34 elukhetfweni lwendlulamitsi lwanga-2016, ngesikhatsi bantfu labangu-66% bavota.
"Ngite kutewuvota ngebantfwana bami, ngendzawo yetfu eYurophu", kusho Gjose Tanevski, umvoti wase Skopje loneminyaka lengu-62.
Zoran Zaev, umengameli wePhalamende yaseMacedonia, umkakhe Zorica nendvodzana yabo Dusko, bavota kuvota kwelibito lelidolobha laseMacedonia kute kuvalwe indlela yekungena e-NATO nase-European Union.
Vladimir Kavardarkov, loneminyaka lengu-54, wenta luhambo loluncane embikwephalamende yaseSkopje, wadvonsa titulo takhe ethendeni lebelisungulwe ngulabo lebebabhikisha.
"Sisekela iNATO ne-EU, kepha sifuna kungena ngemakhanda etfu aphakeme, hhayi ngekungena ngemnyango wetisebenti", kusho Kavadarkov.
"Silive leliphuyile, kodvwa sinesithunzi.
Nangabe awufuni kusemukela njengaseMacedonia, singaya kulamanye emave lafana neChina neRussia, futsi singenela kuhlanganiswa kwe-Eurasia.
Ndvunankhulu Zaev utsi kuba lilunga le-NATO eMacedonia, lapho khona lizinga lekungasebenti lingetulu kwa-20%, kutawuheha lutfo loludzingeka kakhulu.
"Ngiyetsemba kutsi linyenti litawusekela, ngobe ngetulu kwa 80% webantfu bakitsi basekela i-EU ne-NATO", kusho Zaev ngemuva kwekubeka livoti lakhe.
Watsi umphumela waloko "Kube kucinisekisa likusasa letfu".
Ngekusho kwemiphumela yelucwaningo lwelitiko lelitiko letembusave laseMacedonia, lolushicilelwe ngeMsombuluko, kuba khona kwebavoti kulelovoti kufanele kube ngu-30% kuya ku-43%  ngaphansi kwemkhawulo lofunekako.
Ngekusho kwalolunye luhlolo lolwentiwe yi-Telema, bantfu labangu-57% batawuvota ngeLisontfo.
Labangu-70 ekhulwini batsi batawuvota ngaYebo.
Kute kube nemphumelelo, kumele kube nekubakhona kwebavoti labangu-50% kanye nelivoti linye.
