Bonkhe bafundzi labangu-68% batfola ema-A laphakeme.
Lemininingwane lebutfwe etikolweni letingu-74 letiyincenye ye-SCIS ikhombise kutsi bafundzi labangu-72% batfole ema-A laphakeme ekuhlolweni kwabo kwesiMandarin, 72% batfole ema-A laphakeme ekuhlolweni kwabo kwesiJalimane, 69% batfola ema-A laphakeme ekuhlolweni kwabo kwesiFulentji, kantsi 63% batfola ema-A laphakeme ekuhlolweni kwabo kwesiSpanish.
Loku kukhombisa kutsi tikolwa letitimele eScotland titsatsa kufundza tilwimi tangaphandle njengelwati lolubalulekile loludzingwa bantfwana kanye nebantfu labasha esikhatsini lesitako.
Tilwimi njengesifundvo lesifunwako nyalo setibekwa njengentfo lebalulekile etinhlelweni tetikolo letitimele nakuletinye tifundvo letisembili (Isayensi, teTheknoloji, teNgungcondvo kanye neTibalo).
Ngekusho kwelucwaningo lwe-UK Commission for Employment and Skills lwanga-2014, tinkinga tetilwimi letincane betitfolakala ku-17 ekhulwini tetizatfu letenta kube matima kutsi bacashi bagcwalise imisebenti.
Ngako-ke, emakhono elulwimi aya ngekuya abalulekile kute bantfu labasha bakulungele umsebenti wabo.
Njengobe kutfola umsebenti esikhatsini lesitako kutawuba nelulwimi, lamakhono aya ngekuba yimfuneko kulelive lelibuswa ngulamanye emave.
Nobe ngabe ngumuphi umsebenti umuntfu lawukhetsako ekufundzeni lulwimi lwesibili, utawuba nemandla lamakhulu esikhatsini lesitako nangabe anawo lamakhono latawudzingeka ekuphileni kwakhe konkhe.
Umuntfu lowati tilwimi letinyenti utawuba nemandla ekuchudzelana nebantfu bakulamanye emave.
Ngekusho kwelucwaningo lwe-YouGov lwanga-2013 lolwentiwe kubantfu labadzala labangetulu kwa-4 000 base-UK, emaphesenti langu-75 ebantfu bebangakwati kukhuluma lulwimi lolungakalungi kahle kute bangenele ingcoco, kantsi siFulentji bekulululwimi kuphela lolukhulunywa ngelinani lelisetulu lebantfu labangu-15%, lokusho kutsi, emaphesenti langu-15 ebantfu.
Kungako kubalulekile kutsi sitsenge imali ekufundziseni tilwimi kubantfwana bakhona.
Nangabe bantfwana bakhuluma tilwimi letinyenti, ikakhulukati emaveni lasatfutfuka, batawuba nematfuba lamanyenti ekutfola umsebenti lokahle.
Etikolweni taseScotland, tilwimi letifundziswa kuto tehlukile.
Tinyenti tikolwa letigcile etilwimini tesimanje, kantsi letinye tifundzisa tilwimi letibonakala tibalulekile e-UK ngekubuka likusasa langa-2020, njengesiMandarin nesiJapane.
Nobe ngabe ngumiphi imikhuba yemntfwana wakho, kutawuhlala kunetilwimi letinyenti longakhetsa kuto esikolweni lesimele lesinabo bothishela kanye netati.
Tikolwa letitimele taseScotland tikulungele kwakha simondzawo sekufundza lesitawenta bantfwana kutsi bakwati kuphila kahle esikhatsini lesitako.
Akungabateki kutsi emmangweni webhizinisi walamuhla tilwimi tisolo tibalulekile ekusaseni lelive, ngako-ke kudzingeka kutsi tibonakale eluhlelweni lwetfu lwekufundzisa.
Ecinisweni, tilwimi talamuhla kufanele ticatjangwe njengelwati lwekukhulumisana nemave emhlaba.
