Ngusiphi sikhatsi saleli-awa lesitawuba khona inkhulumo yaTrump eNshonalanga yeVirginia, futsi singayibukela njani ku-inthanethi?
Inkhulumo lemfishane leseWilling, eVirginia leseNshonalanga, lehlelelwe kusihlwa nga-7:00 ntsambama, ngeMgcibelo, September 29, 2018, ngesikhatsi saseMpumalanga.
Ungamukela inkhulumo yaTrump ku-inthanethi ku-YouTube.
Lomusho utawutsintsa umcashi weNkantolo lePhakeme kuleliviki, Brett Kavanaugh, njengobe ahlanganise umfutfo lomkhulu ngetinsolo tekutiphatsa kabi ngekwelicansi ngesikhatsi liKhomishane leMalunga eMkhandlu weTifundza livota kumisa kukhetfwa kwemcashi kuze kuphele liviki, ngesikhatsi i-FBI icwaninga.
Kodvwa umgomo loyinhloko walomkhankhaso  kusita emaRephabliki kutsi abe nemandla njengobe kukhetfwa kwaNovemba kusondzela.
Ngako-ke, umkhankaso waMengameli Trump utsi lenhloso yalemihlangano lesihlanu ngeliviki lelitako, njengobe kubikwa yi-Reuters, kutsi ibe "ngukukhutsata emavolontiya kanye nebasekeli, njengobe emaRephabliki etama kuvikela nekukhulisa linyenti lawo eSenate naseNdlini yeBamele".
"Kulawula iCongress kubaluleke kakhulu eluhlelweni lwakhe, futsi Mengameli utawuhamba aye etindzaweni letinyenti njengobe sikhatsi sekukhankasa sishisa kakhulu", kusho sikhulumi semkhankhaso waTrump, lebesingafuni kukhuluma ngeligama.
Inkhulumo yakhe leyabanjwa kusihlwa eWesbank Arena yaseWashington, DC, itawutsatsa bantfu base-Ohio nasePennsylvania futsi itawutsatsa nemitfombo yetindzaba yasePittsburgh, kusho i-Metro News yaseWest Virginia.
NgaLesihlanu, Trump utawuhambela eWest Virginia kwesibili kulenyanga, indzawo latfola kuyo emaphesenti langetulu kwa-40 ekuvota nga-2016.
Trump wetama kusita umholi weWest Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, lobekahleti phansi kakhulu.
"Loku akusiko kuhle kuMorrissey kutsi lomengameli afike kute amkhombise kutsi nguye loyinhloko", kusho Simon Heather, losati setembusave eNyuvesi yase West Virginia, njengoba kubikwa yiReuters.
Umdlalo weRyder Cup wanga-2018: Licembu laseMelika lifuna kuba nemandla futsi lifuna kungena emdlalweni welicembu ngeLisontfo
Ngemuva kwetincenye letintsatfu teMidlalo yeBantfu ngeMgcibelo ntsambama, emacembu lamane angahle abe nguloko lebekudzingeka kulomdlalo weNdzebe yeRyder.
Lokuhleleka lokuhlelekile kungumbono nje, kodvwa bantfu labadlalako bayakukholelwa, ikakhulukati emidlalweni lenjengaleli.
Ngako-ke, ngubani lonenhlanhla nyalo?
"Base bahamba embili ngemaphuzu lasitfupha, nyalo sebahola ngemaphuzu lamane, ngako-ke ngicabanga kutsi singabatsatsa njengemphumelelo", kusho Jordan Spieth, alungiselela lusuku.
Kuliciniso kutsi iYurophu iyahola, inemaphuzu lamane ekudlala futsi inemidlalo lengu-12 lesasele.
Ngekusho kwaSpieth, intsandvo yemaMelika seyiphelile, futsi nabo bayayitsandza, kungasaphatfwa-ke ngendlela Spieth naJustin Thomas labadlala ngayo lilanga lonkhe, futsi ngamunye wabo wazuza emaphuzu lamatsatfu kulamane.
Spieth bekangeke ancotjwe kusukela ekucaleni kute kube sekugcineni futsi bekangumholi loncono.
Njengobe lomjikelo uchubeka, lomsindvo wekuncoba wachubeka, futsi Thomas watfola emaphoyinti lamabili kulokungaba mabili, njengobe bekasondzelene.
Umgodzi wakhe we-15 lowaba nemandla ekubaphumisa, wawuhambisana nemsindvo lofanana nalona lowawuveta kutsi live laseMelika lisengakefiki ekugcineni.
"Kufanele unake kakhulu futsi unake kakhulu umdlalo wakho", kusho Spieth.
Nyalo, bonkhe labadlali kufanele badlale bodvwa.
18 ngemgodzi kute kube sekupheleni.
Badlali labodvwa lababe nemaphuzu lamanyenti kuna Spieth na Thomas kulamalanga lambalwa lambalwa, ngu Francesco Molinari na Tommy Fleetwood, umlandvo longenakucatjangwa we Ryder Cup.
Labashadikazi baseYurophu labangajwayelekile kodvwa labatsandzekako batfole emaphuzu lamane kulokune, futsi bangaphumula.
Bekuyindvodza nemfati labangazange basidzinge sidzakwa nje kuphela ngeMgcibelo ntsambama, kodvwa nangemgcibelo ekuseni, ngeLesihlanu ntsambama nangekuseni ngeLesihlanu.
Loku lokwenteka kanye nendlela bantfu labakhombise ngayo kutsi bayati kutsi batawuba ngulabadlali labatawuphumelela ngeLisontfo, futsi kute lomunye lotawutfola ludvumo njengaFleetwood nobe Molinari, labanelitfuba lekutsi iNational Golf Club incobe eYurophu ngenca yemisebe yekugcina yelanga.
Kungaba kuhle kutsi bagcine sebaphume bobabili ngesikhatsi sinye.
Nanobe kusesekusenesikhatsi kutsi sikhulume ngebuhle baseYurophu.
Bubba Watson na Webbs Simpson badlala sikhashana na Sergio Garcia, umlingisi waseMpumalanga wemaBhola lamane ngesikhatsi ahlanganiswa na Alex Noren.
Umdlalo wekuphindza kabili kanye nemidlalo lemibili yekuphindza kabili kumatsatfu ekucala, wafaka emaSpanish nemaSweden esimeni lesimatima.
Kodvwa kute longasusa tinkinga ngeLisontfo.
Emabhola lamane kanye nemabhola lamane kumnandzi kuwabuka ngenca yekusebentisana kwabo, ngeteluleko labatinikako naletingabaniki, nangekutsi emacebo abo angashintja ngekushesha.
I-Europe beyingcono njengelicembu, ngako-ke beyihola kakhulu ekufikeni kwayo ekugcineni, kepha lomdlalo wema-quarterfinal uphindze wakhombisa kutsi licembu laseMelika linemgogodla wekulwa, lokwaphikiswa ngulabanye, ikakhulukati emaveni.
Ngelilanga lekugcina lemidlalo ye-Ryder Cup, i-Europe seyihola nga-10-6.
IYurophu itawudlala ngelilanga lekugcina lemidlalo yeRyder Cup, ibe sezingeni lelisetulu, ngemuva kwekubamba lichaza ngeMgcibelo kuma-quarter-finals, ibe sezingeni lelisetulu nge-10-6 kunemave aseMelika.
Lendlela yekukhutsata yaTommy Fleetwood naFrancesco Molinari yachubeka nekushisa umoya ngekuncoba kabili Tiger Woods lobekanenkinga, futsi yaholela kuLe Golf National ngemaphuzu lamane.
Emacembu aseYurophu lasembili aThomas Bjorn, afuna kugcina umklomelo wawo lowalahleka eHazeltine eminyakeni lemibili leyendlulile, asebentisa emagama lamane ekuseni kute alwe nemacembu aseMelika labekadze angenele umdlalo futsi aphetsa luhlelo lwawo nga-3:1.
I-USA ikhombise kutimisela lokukhulu emidlalweni lemine, incobe imidlalo lemibili, kepha yehluleka kuncoba umchudzelwano wemaphuzu
Incenye yaJim Furyk idzinga emaphoyinti lasiphohlongo emdlalo welibhola letinyawo longema-12 ngeLisontfo kute igcine letindondo.
Fleetwood waba wekucala eYurophu kutsi atfole emaphoyinti lamane lalandzelanako ngesikhatsi ahlanganiswa naMolinar ku-Mollywood ngemuva kwempelasonto lejabulisako, futsi baba yincenye yesibili yebantfu lababili labatfole emaphoyinti lamane ekucaleni kwemidlalo yabo lemine emlandvweni we-Ryder Cup.
Ngemuva kwekuncoba boWoods naPatrick Reed kuma-four-man, bacedza ngekushesha boWoods labesebancane ngekwetsemba kanye naBryson Dechambeau waseMelika ngekuncintisana lokuncono kakhulu, nga-5:4.
Woods, lowancoba emacembu lamabili ngeMgcibelo, wakhombisa lizinga lelisetulu lebuchwepheshe, kodvwa besekadze alahlekelwe ngu-19 kuya ku-29 emacembu akhe lamane, lasikhombisa alandzelana.
Justin Rose waphumula ekuseni ngentsimbi yesine wase ubuyela emuva wadlala nemlingani wakhe Henrik Stenson ngentsimbi yesine; bancoba 2:1 2&1 Dustin Johnson na Brooks Koepke, lababili labadlala indzima yekucala neyesitsatfu emhlabeni.
Nanobe bekulilanga lelihle futsi linemoya lovutsako eningizimu-nshonalanga yeParis, tintfo betingahambi kahle eYurophu.
Umdlali lowina emahlandla lamatsatfu Jordan Spieth naJustin Thomas bahola emaMelika ngekutfola emaphuzu lamabili ngeMgcibelo.
Emdlalweni wemabhola lamane, bancoba ngekuncoba lokumatima nga 2:1 ku John Rahm na Ian Poulter base Spain, kantsi emdlalweni wesine bancoba Poulter na Rory McIlroy nga 4:3, bangakafaki ibhola emaceleni ekucala lamabili.
Kwekuphela kwesikhatsi letimbili emlandvweni we Ryder Cup lapho khona licembu likwatile kulwisana nekubamba emaphoyinti lamane ekudlala emdlalweni munye, nanobe incenye yaFuryko beyinelibhola lelingene lekugcina umklomelo.
Nanobe bebabalwa njengebantfu lababili, kodvwa ngeLisontfo, inhlanhla yabo yabonakala seyiphelile.
