Ri wacaphuna sitatimende lesihlangene lesentiwa ngu Kim Jong Un na Donald Trump ngesikhatsi bahlangana kwekucala umengameli waseMelika kanye nemholi wase North Korea eSingapore nga June 12, lapho khona Kim watetsembisa kusebenta ngekulwa nekuhlukunyetwa kweKorean Peninsula, kantsi Trump watetsembisa kuvikela iNorth Korea.
INyakatfo Korea ifuna kuphela kwemphi yaseKorea yanga-1950-53, kepha iMelika itsi kwekucala iPyongyang kufanele ilahle tikhali tayo te-nuclear.
I-Washington nayo ayifuni kunciphisa kucindzetelwa lokukhulu kwe-North Korea.
"I-USA icondze kutsi kube khona kukhululeka kwenyukliya kucala futsi ikhulisa kucindzeteleka ngekubekwa kwekucindzetelwa kute ifinyelele umgomo wayo ngetindlela tebudlova, ngisho nangesikhatsi ingasatifaki tandla ekumenyeteleni kuphela kwemphi", kusho Ri.
Kucabanga kutsi singancishwa tinhlawulo kufana nekulandzela emaphupho langasiwo ebantfu lesingabanaki.
Inkinga kutsi kucinisela kwaletindlela tekucindzetela kucinisa kungetsembi kwetfu.
Ri akazange akhulume ngeluhlelo lwekuhlangana kwesibili kwaKim naTrump, lokwavetwa ngumholi waseMelika e-UN ekucaleni kwaleliviki.
Esikhundleni saloko, lomengameli wagcizelela imihlangano lemitsatfu emkhatsini waKim neMholi waseNingizimu Korea, Moon Jae-in, etinyangeni letisihlanu letengcile: "Kube lelinye live lebelikhuluma ngaloludzaba lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo lwekulwa neluvivinyo".
Kodvwa indlela Ri lebekhuluma ngayo yashintja kakhulu kusukela emnyakeni lowengcile ngesikhatsi atjela uMhlangano Jikelele we-UN kutsi ngesikhatsi Mengameli Trump abita Kim ngekutsi ngumnumzane wemakhemikhali lowenta umsebenti wekubulala, kucondziswa kwemakhemikhali aseNyakatfo Korea kuya eMelika bekungeke kuphele.
Kulomnyaka e-UN, Trump, lowesabise kutsi utawucedza i-North Korea yonkhe, wadvumisa Kim ngesibindzi sakhe sekutfutfukisa kuhlulwa kwetikhali, kodvwa watsi kusekuningi lokusamele kwentiwe nekutsi kuvinjelwa kumele kuhlale kukhona kute kube ngulapho i-North Korea ifinyelela ezingeni lekuhlulwa kwetikhali.
NgaLesitsatfu, Trump watsi kute sikhatsi lesimisiwe, watsi kungatsatsa iminyaka lemibili, iminyaka lemitsatfu nobe tinyanga letisihlanu, akukhatsaleki.
I-China neRussia batsi Umkhandlu Wetekuphepha Wemave Emhlaba kumele ubhubhise iPyongyang ngetento tayo.
Nanobe kunjalo, Ndvunankhulu waseMelika Mike Pompeo, watsi eMkhandlwini Wetekuphepha we-UN ngeLesine, "tijeziso te-UN kumele tihlale ticinile futsi tinganiketwa kute kube ngulapho sekugcwaliswe ngalokuphelele kucedvwa kwetikhali te-nuclear".
UMkhandlu weTekuphepha wavumelana ngemvume kutsi kube netinhlawulo letibhekiswe eNyakatfo Korea kusukela nga-2006 kute kuvinjelwe kutfola imali yekusekela tinhlelo te-nuclear kanye netebhalisi.
Pompeo wahlangana naRi ngemuva kwe-UN General Assembly wase utsi utawuvakashela iPyongyang futsi ngenyanga letako kute ahlele umhlangano lolandzelako.
Pompeo uvakashele eNyakatfo Korea katsatfu kulomnyaka, kodvwa luhambo lwakhe lwekugcina aluzange luphumelele.
NgaJuly, waphuma ePyongyang atsi konkhe loku bekwentelwe kutsi emahora lambalwa ngemuva kwaloko iNorth Korea imemetele kutsi seyifake ticelo teligenge.
Ngesikhatsi ihlangana naMoon kulenyanga, iNyakatfo Korea yetsembisa kucedza indzawo yayo yemakhemikhali kanye nenchubo yayo yenyukliya uma iMelika itsatsa tinyatselo letifanele.
Ngekusho kwakhe, Kim watsi letindlela letifanele abefuna kutifinyelela tifaka ekhatsi kucinisekisa kuphepha lokwavetwa nguTrump eSingapore kanye nekwenta budlelwane neWashington bube busesimeni lesifanele.
Bafundzi baseHarvard bafundza kutfola sikhatsi lesenele sekuphumula
Sifundvo lesisha eHarvard University kulomnyaka sikhutsate bonkhe bafundzi kutsi balale kakhulu kute kulwiswane nenkholo yemadvodza lekhulako, lefaka ekhatsi kusebentisa kakhulu i-caffeine kanye nekungalali kahle.
Lomunye umfundzi utfole kutsi etikolweni letiphakeme kakhulu emhlabeni wonkhe, bafundzi bavame kungabi nalwati lolusisekelo lwekutiphatsa.
Charles C. Cheisler, longulomunye wabochwephesha betekwelapha butfongo eHarvard Medical School, kanye naBrigam Sitish, losebenta eSibhedlela Sabomake, bakha sifundvo labatsi siba kwekucala eMelika.
Umcondvo wekwenta lenkhundla wavela ngemuva kwekukhuluma ngemiphumela yekungalali kahle ekufundzeni.
Ekugcineni, lomunye umfana weta kimi watsi, "Kwentiwa yini kutsi loku kungitjele mine nyalo, ngesikhatsi ngisemnyakeni wami wekugcina?"
Watsi kute umuntfu lowake wamtjela ngekubaluleka kwekulala, futsi loko kwangimangalisa", asho njalo kuThe Telegraph.
Lolu luhlelo lwekucala loluniketwa kulomnyaka, luchaza bafundzi kutsi indlela yekulala leyecile ibaluleke kangakanani ekuzuzeni imiphumela kutemfundvo, kutemidlalo kanye nasekutiveni kahle.
Paul Barreira, longulomunye wabophrofesa betemphilo yengcondvo futsi longumphatsi lomkhulu we-University Health Services eHarvard Medical School, watsi leyonyuvesi yakhetsa kuniketa bafundzi leliklasi ngemuva kwekubona kutsi bafundzi babo bebangaphumeleli kulala kahle liviki lonkhe.
Lenkhosi lehlala li-awa linye ifaka ekhatsi luhlu lwemisebenti lechubekako.
Kulenye incenye kunesitfombe sendlu yekuhlala lapho bafundzi bangachofoza khona etikhofini, emakhethini, etincwadzini tekufundza nekwenta umsebenti kute bafundze nge-caffeine, umtselela wekukhanya, indlela kungalali kahle lokutsintsa ngayo kutivocavoca kanye nekubaluleka kwekulala.
Kulomunye umhlangano, bafundzi bafundza kutsi kungalali sikhatsi lesidze kungakhulisa bungoti bekushaywa yinhlitiyo, sifo sengcondvo, kucindzeteleka kanye nemdlavuza.
Lemephu yelikhampasi lenetiphikikhodi letichumanako leticinisekisa kutsi bafundzi bayaticabanga tintfo labatentako.
Siyabona kutsi loku angeke kusishintje simo sebantfwana ngekushesha.
Kodvwa sicabanga kutsi banelilungelo lekwati - njengobe nawe unalo lilungelo lekwati ngemiphumela yetemphilo yekukhetsa kubhema", kuchaza Phrofesa Ceisler.
Utsi: "Sisolo sikhona lesimo sekungalali ebusuku, futsi buchwepheshe kanye nekucindzetelwa lokunyenti lokuchubekako kulabantfwana sekubangele kutsi bantfu labanyenti bangakhoni kulala.
Kucinisekisa kutsi balala kahle kufanele kube sikhali lesiyimfihlo sebafundzi ekulweni nekucindzeteleka, kukhatsateka kanye nekukhatsateka, watsi, ngisho nobe bangafuni kuba nesisindvo, ngobe kungalali kahle kuvula ingcondvo yabo kutsi ingalali kahle, ngako bafundzi bahlala balambile.
Raymond So, umfana waseCalifornia loneminyaka lengu-19 budzala lofundza ngekwakheka kwetintfo kanye ne-physical biology, wasita Phrofesa Ceisler kutsi akhe sifundvo sakhe ngesikhatsi ahambela sifundvo sakhe sekucala eHarvard emnyakeni lowengcile.
Watsi lesifundvo samvula emehlo futsi samkhutsata kutsi afune sifundvo lesingavulelwa bonkhe bafundzi.
Ufuna kutsi loluhlelo lwekucala lucele bonkhe bafundzi labafundza emabanga laphakeme kutsi bafundze ngaphambi kwekutsi bacale kufundza kulesi sikhungo lesibukene nalomncintiswano.
Phrofesa Czeisler weluleka bafundzi kutsi basebentise i-alamu yabo yekulala njengobe benta nasekuvukeni kwabo, futsi bacaphele kukhanya lokuluhlata sasibhakabhaka lokukhishwa tintfo tebuchwephesha kanye netibane letikhanyako, ngobe kungenta umtimba wakho ungabi nemsindvo futsi kube matima kulala.
Umdlalo waManga wabadzabukisa kakhulu bantfu baGerard.
I-Rangers yabhekana nalokunye kudvumateka ngesikhatsi Dolly Mengi Livingstone ancoba umlingisi lowalimala kakhulu Steven Gerrard nga 1-0.
Ibrox beyilindzele kuncoba kwekucala kuloluhambo ngemuva kwekuncoba kwabo ngaFebruary 4-1 ku St Johnstone, kepha licembu laGary Holt lamehlula Gerrard kwesibili ngemuva kwemidlalo lengu-18 njengengameli, futsi nyalo leli qembu selivele lisemuva ngemaphuzu lasiphohlongo kunebadlali be Premier League labakhashane kakhulu, iHearts.
Meng wafaka umgomo ngemizuzu lesikhombisa ngaphambi kwekuphela kwekuphela, kodvwa i-Rangers lebeyingakhutsateki, ayizange ibone litfuba lekwenta umdlalo ube silinganiso.
I Rangers seyihlele endzaweni yesitfupha, i Livingston seyifinyelele endzaweni yesitsatfu, seyihamba ngemuva kwe Hibernian ngemagoli lambalwa.
Kodvwa loko akusiko kuphela kwekukhatsateka kweRangers ngobe intfo lebeyibekwe etulu etitulwini, yahlasela inhloko yeMehluleli Calum Spence, yamlimata.
Gerrard wenta tingucuko letine letamenta kutsi adlule i-Ireland futsi amyisa ku-Betfred Cup semifinal.
