UMengameli waseMelika Donald Trump wakhuluma ngeLwesitsatfu lolendlulile ngesincwajana se-China Daily, lesiphatselene ne-Des Moines Register, iphephandaba lelibaluleke kakhulu e-Iowa, futsi wasola iChina ngekusebentisa emandla ayo kute itsintse lukhetfo lwe-US Congress loluhlelelwe umhlaka-6 Lweti.
Kugceka kwaTrump ngekutsi iBeijing yetama kutsintsa lukhetfo lwaseMelika kukhombisa sigaba lesisha semkhankhaso waseWashington wekucinisa kucindzetela iChina, kusho tiphatsimandla taseMelika kuReuters.
Nanobe kuvamile kutsi bohulumende bangaphandle basakata tikhangiso kute bakhutsate kuhwebelana, kodvwa iBeijing neWashington nyalo sebangenele imphi yekuhweba, futsi bobabili babhekene netindleko tekungenisa tintfo kulamanye emave.
