"Kuhambisa inkhulumo-manga, hulumende waseChina usebentise inkhululeko yekukhuluma kanye neyekushicilela lehlonishwa eMelika, futsi watfumela sikhangiso lesikhokhelwayo eDes Moines Register", kubhala Branstad.
