Kutfunyelwa kwesikebhe lesisha semphi yaseJalimane sekucitsekile futsi
Lelinye libutfo lemphi lelisandza kutalwa beliniketwe umsebenti wekuvala timphahla letatisetjentiswa ngeminyaka yeliWundlu laseJalimane nga-2014, kodvwa ngekusho kwetindzaba tasekhaya, angeke libonwe kuze kube ngulomnyaka lotako ngenca yetintfo letingahambi kahle kanye netindleko letinyenti.
Ngekusho kwesikhulumi semabutfo, lesicashunwe yi-Die Zeit, Rheinland-Pfalz  umkhonto wekucalisa kusebenta wesikebhe lesisha lesingumkhumbi we-Baden-Württemberg  nyalo sewubekelwe inyanga yekucala yanga-2019.
Lomkhumbi bekufanele ungenele umbutfo wetimphi ngemnyaka wa 2014, kepha likusasa laloluhlelo lolukhulu lavalwa tinkinga lebetibangwa ngulomkhumbi lowatsengiswa.
Tintfo letine telibanga le-Baden-Württemberg, letatsengwa ngemkhumbi ngemnyaka wa 2007, titawuvala sikhala semkhumbi lomdzala welibanga le-Bremen.
Kucatjangwa kutsi letindiza titawuhlanganisa umshini lomkhulu wekubika, ema-anti-aircraft kanye nemishini yekulwa nemikhumbi, kanye nelwati lolutsite lolungekho emtsetfweni, njengekucedza kubonwa kwetintfo letisebenta nge-radar, i-infrared kanye nemsindvo.
Lokunye lokubalulekile  sikhatsi lesidze sekugadza, lokwenta kutsi emafrigate lamasha akwati kuhamba iminyaka lemibili.
Nanobe kunjalo, ngekusho kwa-Die Zeit, ngenca yekubambezeleka, letitfombe letisezingeni lelisetulu letitintfo letingasita iJalimane kutsi ikwati kubeka emandla ayo emphini etindzaweni letingetulu kwemhlaba, titawucala kuguga.
Lelisu lelihlulekile i-F125 laba setindzabeni temlandvo ngemnyaka lophelile ngesikhatsi libutfo lemphi laseJalimane liyekela kusebentisa leliketselo futsi libuyisa leliketsiso emashini ekwakha imikhumbi i-Blohm & Voss eHamburg.
Loku kwekucala kutsi libutfo lemphi libuyisele umkhumbi lowentiwe.
Kute lokwatiko ngesizatfu sekubuyiselwa emuva, kodvwa emaphepheni aseJalimane kukhulunywa ngetinkinga letinkhulu letitsite letenteka kuloluhlelo kanye netintfo letitsite letingaba nemiphumela lengakalindzeleki.
Tinkinga letibalulekile letitsintsa i-software, ngobe imikhumbi ye-Baden-Württemberg itawusetjentiswa ngemalunga emkhumbi langu-120  lokusho kutsi kutawuba luhlangotsi lunye kuphela lwemkhumbi kunemikhumbi yakadzeni ye-Bremen.
Ngetulu kwaloko, lomkhumbi wawubonakala unesisindvo lesisetulu kakhulu  lokwenta kutsi ungabi nemphumelelo futsi kunciphise emandla emkhumbi kutsi usebentise tintfo letitsite letitfutfukisako esikhatsini lesitako.
Kucatjangwa kutsi i-Rheinland-Pfalz lenemathani langu-7 000 inesisindvo lesiphindvwe kabili kunesicumbi semikhumbi lefanako lebeyisetjentiswa ngemaJalimane eMphini Yelive Yesibili.
Tindleko talomklamo  kanye netintfo tekusebenta letilahlekile, kufaka ekhatsi kuceceshwa kwebasebenti  nako sekuya ngekuba yinkinga.
Kubikwa kutsi seyiye yakhula kusuka ku-euro letinkhulungwane letingu-2,2 kuya ku-euro letinkhulungwane letingu-3,1 (emarandi latigidzi letingu-3,6).
Tinkinga letisandza kwenteka letitsintsa lelibhomu letinkhulu tibonakala kakhulu ngemuva kwetinsolo tekwehla kwemandla emphi yaseJalimane.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, Hans-Peter Bartels, loyinhloko yelikomidi lekuvikela ePhalamende yaseJalimane, wavuma kutsi vele libutfo lemphi liyaswela imikhumbi lekhona kuyisebentisa.
Lesisebenti satsi tinkinga betisolo tikhona ngobe imikhumbi leyayisele seyiphelile, kodvwa kute lebekungafakwa esikhundleni sayo.
Wavuma kutsi kute ngisho munye umkhumbi weBaden-Württemberg longakhoni kungena emkhunjini.
