Kuhlolwa kwato tonkhe timphawu temsindvo letibhalwe ngulabanye beluleki kutawukhombisa kutsi emalulwane avame kangakanani kusakata futsi enta njani.
Lendlela yekwakha indzawo yekuhlala itawube seyivele ikhona kanye nembiko lotawusita kwakha sitfombe sekutiphatsa lokunemininingwane kulo lonkhe lelive.
Rob Dewar, longumeluleki wetindzawo tekulondvolota e-National Trust for Scotland (NTS), wetsemba kutsi imiphumela itawukhombisa kutsi ngutiphi tindzawo letibalulekile kubologwaja nekutsi tilusebentisa njani loluhlobo.
Lolwati lutakusita ekuboneni tinzuzo tekunakekela tindzawo tekuhlala, njengekwakhiwa kwemahlatsi, kanye nekutfola indlela lekahle yekunakekela tindzawo temahlatsi kute tibe tindzawo letikahle tekuhlala tilwanyana kanye naletinye tinhlobo letihlobene nato.
