Brexit: iUK itawuhlale ililela kutsi ilahlekelwe bakhiciti betimoto
Ngekusho kwaNobhala weTemabhizinisi, Greg Clark, iUK itawuphindze ilimale nangabe ilahlekelwa sikhundla sayo sekuba ngumholi wemhlaba wonkhe wekukhicita timoto ngemuva kweBrexit.
Wengeta ngekukhatsateka ngekusho kwe-BBC kutsi uma i-UK ingakhoni kukhipha i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano, umkhicito utawumiswa kwesikhashana eBurnaston, ngase Derby.
"Sidzinga sivumelwano", kwasho Mnu Clark.
Lomkhicito wemoto waseJapan watsi kulahlekelwa yimisebenti kutawuba khona uma ngabe 'i-Brexit' ingekho.
Umkhicito waseBurnestone, lowenta ema-Toyota Auris ne-Avensis, wakhicita cishe timoto letingu-150 000 emnyakeni lowengcile, lokungaba ngu-90% wato letatfunyelwa kulamanye emave aseYurophu.
"Ngicabanga kutsi uma iBritain ishiya i-European Union ngekushesha ekupheleni kwaMarch, sitokoleka kutsi siyekele kukhicita", kusho umphatsi lomkhulu weToyota eBurnastone, Marvin Cook.
Labanye bakhiciti betimoto base-UK, lokufaka ekhatsi Honda, BMW, Jaguar kanye Land Rover nabo bakhulume ngekukhatsateka ngekuphuma kwe-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano kanye nemiphumela yako kutekuhweba kwemave emhlaba.
Sibonelo, iBMW itsi itawuvala ifektri yayo yaseMini ngemuva kwenyanga iBrexit iphelile.
Ngekusho kwebakhiciti betimoto, lokubaluleke kakhulu kutsi kunetinsongo letingaba khona kuloluhlaka lwekuphakela uma ngabe i-Brexit ingekho.
Loluhlaka lwekukhicita lwe-Toyota lusebenta ngesikhatsi lesifanele, ngobe tincenye temoto letakhiwe ngesincumo tifika njalo ngemaminitsi langu-37 tisuka e-UK nakulamanye emave lakhelene nalo.
Nangabe i-UK ishiya i-EU ingenawo umtsetfo ngaMarch 29, kutawuba netinkinga emnyeleni, futsi labosomabhizinisi batsi loko kutawenta kutsi kube nekubambezeleka nobe kungabi khona kwemininingwane.
 Toyota yatsi ifemu yase Derbyshire angeke ikhone kugcina tintfo letingaba yintfo ledzingekako ngelilanga linye, ngako-ke umkhicito utawumiswa.
Ngekusho kwaClark, luhlelo lwa Theresa May lwe 'Chequers' lwekusebenta ne EU lusungulwe ngendlela yekutsi kungabi khona kuhlolwa lokunjalo eminyeleni.
"Sidzinga inkontileka. Sifuna kuba nenkontileka lencono kakhulu lengenta kutsi, njengobe ngishito, singagcini ngekutfola imphumelelo lamuhla, kodvwa sisebentise lelitfuba", washo kulenhlelo ye-BBC Radio 4 i-Today.
Leti tibonakaliso akusito teToyota kuphela kodvwa netalabanye bakhiciti betimoto tikhombisa kutsi kubalulekile kuchubeka nekusebentisa luhlelo loluphumelele kakhulu lwekuhlanganisa tintfo.
Toyota beyingakhoni kusho kutsi kutawumiswa sikhatsi lesingakanani, kodvwa yacaphela kutsi ngekubuka sikhatsi lesidze, tindleko letengetiwe betitawenta kutsi ifemu ingabi nekuncintisana futsi ekugcineni kube netindleko temisebenti.
Peter Tsouvallaris, losebente iminyaka lengu-24 eBurnestone futsi lowengamele imihlangano ye-UNITE, watsi emalunga akhe etinhlangano atfutfuka ngekukhatsateka: "Kwekubona kwami, uma ngabe ngilahlekelwa ngumsebenti, angeke aphindze awutfole".
Sikhulumi sahulumende satsi: Sinikete luhlelo lolucondzile nalolucinile lwebudlelwane lobutawuba khona ne-EU.
