Kungako ngifuna kuphindze ngivume kutsi ngiyakutsandza kufaka sandla kwabo bonkhe basebenti  kungakhatsaliseki kutsi ngabe bakuliphi live.
Bozakwethu labavela kulo lonkhe le-EU nalamanye emave baletsa lwati lolubalulekile nemakhono lacinisa aphindze ente ncono kusebenta kweluhlelo lwetemphilo, lokuzuzisa tigulane nemiphakatsi lesiyisebentisako.
