Indlela i-US-China Trade Deal lengasita ngayo iBeijing
Imphikiswano yekuhweba emkhatsini weMelika neChina seyicale, futsi nanobe lemphi isengakapheli, tati titsi kungevani kungazuzisa iBeijing.
Mengameli waseMelika Donald Trump wakhipha secwayiso sakhe sekucala kulomnyaka ngekubeka umtselo etikwetintfo letinkhulu letitfunyelwa eChina, kufaka ekhatsi emaseli elanga, insimbi ne-aluminium.
Lokuphikisana lokukhulu kwenteka kuleliviki ngesikhatsi kucalwa kuhlawuliswa imali lemisha yetintfo letibita tigidzigidzi temadola langu-200 (emarandi latigidzigidzi letingu-150) letitawutsatfwa njengentfo lemisha, lokusho kutsi cishe incenye yaloko lokutfunyelwa eMelika yiChina kutawufakwa intsela.
I-Beijing yaphendvula ngalendlela: Ngekukhipha umtsetfo lomusha, yafaka umtselo wa 5% kuya ku 10% etikwetimphahla taseMelika letibita tigidzigidzi letinge-$60.
I-China ifunge kulwa ne-USA ngematinyo, futsi kubonakala shengatsi lelive lelisemakethe yesibili ngobukhulu emhlabeni angeke lihle masinyane.
I-Washington itawunciphisa kuphela uma iChina ihlonipha timfuno tayo, kepha kutfobela i-USA embikwebantfu kutawuba lukhuni kakhulu kuMengameli wase China Xi Jinping.
Nobe kunjalo, tati titsi nangabe iBeijing idlala indzima yayo, tinkinga temphi yekuhwebelana neMelika tingaba nemiphumela lemihle eChina ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi, ngobe kutawehlisa kuhlobana kwalemakethe.
"Kutsi sincumo lesingacondzakali sepolitiki eWashington nobe eBeijing singenta simo lesingabangela umnotfo wato totimbili tive kutsi wehle, kuyingoti kakhulu kunaloko lababukeli labakucaphele", kusho Abigail Grace, losebenta e-Asia Institute's Center for the New American Security.
