Ngesikhatsi akhuluma eMhlanganweni Wetive Wemave Emhlaba, Ndvuna Yetekuhamba, Walid al-Moualem, watsi timo tiyachubeka nekutfutfuka.
"Ngenca yetinhlelo tekulwa nebuphekula, simo sesibe ncono kakhulu futsi sesiphephile", kusho yena.
Baphatsi bayachubeka nekusebenta kute bavuselele simo lesivamile.
Tintfo setentiwe kutsi labo lababalekile babuyele emaveni abo ngekutitsandzela, lapho baphocelelwe khona kutsi bahambe ngenca yebuphekula kanye netigwebo temnotfo tangalolunye luhlangotsi letilimata imphilo yabo yemalanga onkhe kanye nenhlalakahle yabo.
Ngekusho kwe-UN, kusukela kwacala lemphi nga-2011, bantfu baseSiriya labangu-5,5 wetigidzi baphumile.
Bantfu labatigidzi letisitfupha labasaphila kulelive badzinga lusito.
Al-Moualem watsi umbuso waseSyria utawemukela ngelutsandvo lusito lwekwakha kabusha lelive lelibhujisiwe.
Kodvwa waphindze wagcizelela kutsi angeke emukele lusito nobe lusito lolungakalindzeleki kumave lasekela lemphi.
